<HEADLINE> Boeing Employment Down 5.4 Percent </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	SEATTLE (AP) -- New figures from Boeing Co. show a 5.4 percent  
drop in companywide employment so far this year, reducing the 
number of workers at the troubled aerospace giant from 231,260 down 
to 218,700 workers as of April 1. 
