<HEADLINE> Marcia Clark Cleared in Suit </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LOS ANGELES (AP) -- A judge has tossed out a lawsuit claiming  
O.J. Simpson prosecutor Marcia Clark and two former detectives had 
no authority to publish crime-scene photos in their books about the 
