<P>
	Total sales were $2.89 billion, up 17.5 percent from $2.47  
billion. 
</P>
<P>
 *Two months ended April 3: 
</P>
<P>
	Same-store sales rose 11 percent.  
</P>
<P>
	Total sales were $4.91 billion, up 15.8 percent.  
